values.value: SELECT Id, Case__c, RAF_Indicator__c, Agency_Information__r.Name, Client_Name__r.Name FROM Tax_Notice_Index__c WHERE RecordType.Name = 'Manual Indexing' AND Agency_Information__c = : strAgentInfo AND Client_Name__c = : strClientName AND Segment__c = : strSegment AND Tier__c = : strTier AND Partner_Tier__c = : strPartnerTier AND Yr_Qtr__c = : strYearQuarter AND Tax_Notice_Form_Number__c = :strTaxNoticeFormNumber AND Tax_Notice_Date__c = : dtTaxNoticeDate AND Tax_Notice_Type__c = : strTaxNoticeType AND Tax_Notice_Tax_Amount__c = : decTaxAmount AND Tax_Notice_Amount_Total__c = : dbTaxNoticeAmountTotal AND Assigned_Client_Tax_ID_Agency_Assigned__c = : strAgencyAssigned
